	<h2> <center> FAQ </center> </h2>

	<p><strong>Q:</strong> Why can&rsquo;t I post comments or &lsquo;like&rsquo; other user&rsquo;s Pheeling entries?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Phanziety was intentionally designed to give users a forum to express their Pheelings without any kind of feedback from other users within the app itself. However, if you would like to share your Pheelings or have others like/comment, please feel free to use the &lsquo;Share&rsquo; option to post on other social media outlets where comments are encouraged.<br /><strong>Q:</strong> Can I select more than 1 favorite sports team?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Yes. However, we encourage you not to select more than your favorite team per sports category. &nbsp;<br /><strong>Q:</strong> Can I make an entry for a sports team that is not selected as one of my favorites?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Users have the ability to participate in every sporting event available on the Phanziety app. However, to participate in a sporting event that does not involve your selected favorite team, you can submit entries utilizing the &ldquo;Just Watching&rdquo; feature.<br /><strong>Q:</strong> How are coins earned and what are they used for?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Coins are earned every time you participate in an event by selecting an emotion from the Phanziety Pheeling Wheel. Bonus coins are rewarded for things like sharing on other social media platforms. Coins are used for unlocking features within the app. New and exciting features are coming soon with more options to use your coins. <br /><strong>Q:</strong> Can I add Private Events?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Private events will soon be available. For now, please email the Phanziety team at info@phanziety.com to learn more.<br /><strong>Q:</strong> Can I add new emotions (e.g. Happy) as options to select on the Phanziety Pheeling Wheel?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Currently no. You can however submit requests to add new emotions via email to the Phanziety team (info@Phanziety.com).&nbsp;&nbsp; The Phanziety team will consider suggestions for new emotions in the future.<br /><strong>Q:</strong> Can I customize the emojis (e.g. use a personal photo)?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Yes. You will have the opportunity to customize 3 emoji&rsquo;s upon initial download. You must then earn and use coins to unlock the ability to customize additional emoji&rsquo;s. <br /><strong>Q:</strong> What are Phanzults?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Phanzults are tallies of all the Pheelings submitted for an event; where the most commonly selected Pheeling is shown.&nbsp; Sporting events will show 3 different sets of Phanzults.<br /><strong>Q:</strong> Can I change my Pheeling submission after an event starts?<br /><strong>A:</strong> You can modify your submissions as often as you like during the specified time periods; pre-event, during event, and post-event . For instance, once an event starts, the &lsquo;pre-event&rsquo;&nbsp; Phanziety entry box is locked and your latest entry will be saved. <br /><strong>Q:</strong> What if an event in my interest is not available on the Phanziety app?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Please submit event category requests via email to the Phanziety team: info@phanziety.com.&nbsp; All suggestions/requests will be considered for addition in the future.<br /><strong>Q:</strong> Is there an age restriction for using Phanziety? <br /><strong>A:</strong> No, however it is always advisable to seek permission from a parent/guardian before downloading the app if you are under the age of 18. <br /><strong>Q:</strong> Do you have a website?<br /><strong>A:</strong> Yes. The Phanziety website can be found here: www.phanziety.com --- note that all user functionality is only accessible using the mobile app.</p>

